*gruff-0.6.0 (31 May 2015)

  31 May 2015; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> +gruff-0.6.0.ebuild:
  Version bump.

  18 Apr 2015; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> gruff-0.5.1-r1.ebuild:
  imagemagick also needs to support PNG for tests.

  20 Mar 2015; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> gruff-0.5.1-r1.ebuild:
  Add ruby22.

  28 Nov 2014; Manuel Rüger <mrueg@gentoo.org> -gruff-0.3.7.ebuild:
  Cleanup old.

  28 Nov 2014; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> gruff-0.5.1.ebuild:
  Stable for x86, wrt bug #512180

  18 Nov 2014; Manuel Rüger <mrueg@gentoo.org>
  -files/gruff-0.3.6-fix-tests.patch, -files/gruff-0.3.6-sort-filenames.patch,
  -files/gruff-0.3.6-zero-division.patch:
  Cleanup unused patches.

